📅 2-Month DevOps & AWS Learning Plan  
----------------------------------------
⏳ Daily: 2-3 hours of learning & practice  

🟢 Month 1: AWS Fundamentals & Core Services  
----------------------------------------
📌 Week 1: Cloud & Compute Basics  
✅ Day 1-2: Cloud Computing & AWS Basics  
✅ Day 3-4: EC2 (Compute)  
✅ Day 5-6: VPC (Networking)  
✅ Day 7: Hands-on Practice (EC2 in VPC)  

📌 Week 2: AWS Storage Services  
✅ Day 8-9: S3 Buckets & Storage Classes  
✅ Day 10-11: EBS & EFS  
✅ Day 12: Hands-on Practice (S3 & EBS)  
✅ Day 13-14: RDS & DynamoDB  

📌 Week 3: Security & IAM  
✅ Day 15-16: IAM (Users, Roles, Policies)  
✅ Day 17-18: Route 53 (DNS)  
✅ Day 19-20: CloudWatch & CloudTrail  
✅ Day 21: Hands-on Practice  

📌 Week 4: Auto-Scaling & CI/CD Intro  
✅ Day 22-23: Auto-Scaling & Load Balancing  
✅ Day 24-25: AWS DevOps Services (CodePipeline, CodeDeploy)  
✅ Day 26-27: Hands-on Practice  
✅ Day 28: Month 1 Review & Mini Project  

🟢 Month 2: DevOps Tools & CI/CD Pipeline  
----------------------------------------
📌 Week 5: Version Control & CI/CD Basics  
✅ Day 29-30: Git & GitHub  
✅ Day 31-32: Jenkins (CI/CD Automation)  
✅ Day 33-34: Hands-on Practice (CI/CD Pipeline)  

📌 Week 6: Containerization with Docker  
✅ Day 35-36: Docker Basics  
✅ Day 37-38: Docker Compose & Swarm  
✅ Day 39-40: Hands-on Practice (Dockerized App)  

📌 Week 7: Kubernetes & Infrastructure as Code  
✅ Day 41-42: Kubernetes Basics  
✅ Day 43-44: Kubernetes YAML & Scaling  
✅ Day 45-46: Terraform (IaC)  
✅ Day 47-48: Hands-on Practice (K8s on AWS)  

📌 Week 8: Configuration Management & Final Project  
✅ Day 49-50: Ansible (Config Mgmt)  
✅ Day 51-52: Prometheus & Grafana (Monitoring)  
✅ Day 53-54: Hands-on Practice  
✅ Day 55-56: Capstone Project (Complete DevOps Pipeline)  

🎯 **Final Outcomes After 2 Months**  
✅ Strong AWS & DevOps Foundation  
✅ Hands-on Experience with Cloud, Containers & CI/CD  
✅ A Full DevOps Project for Resume & Interview  

